				<h3 id="post-1756"><a href="http://samablog.robsama.com/?p=1756" rel="bookmark" title="Permanent Link to News Coverage">News Coverage</a></h3>
				<small>Thursday, July 29th, 2004</small>

				<div class="entry">
					<p>My blog(s) and I are to be featured in a local newspaper soon, and reporters are coming over to my apartment to photograph me in front of my computer.  So I have some cleaning to do tonight.  I&#8217;ll blog Kerry&#8217;s speech, but probably not much more.</p>
<p>Stay posted for more news on tomorrow&#8217;s event.</p>
				</div>

				<p class="postmetadata"> Posted in <a href="http://samablog.robsama.com/?cat=2" title="View all posts in Announcements" rel="category">Announcements</a> |   <a href="http://samablog.robsama.com/?p=1756#comments" title="Comment on News Coverage">2 Comments &#187;</a></p>

