		<tr><td class="sideboxl">&nbsp;</td>
		<td class="sideboxc">
		<ul>
		<li id="linkcat-12" class="widget widget_links"><h2 class="widgettitle">boston</h2>
	<ul class='xoxo blogroll'>
<li><a href="http://bloggingbelmont.com/">blogging belmont</a></li>
<li><a href="http://www.bostonblogs.com/">boston blogs</a></li>
<li><a href="http://boston.citysearch.com">boston citysearch</a></li>
<li><a href="http://boston.craigslist.org">boston craigslist</a></li>
<li><a href="http://www.bostonphoenix.com">boston phoenix</a></li>
<li><a href="http://www.weeklydig.com/">boston&#8217;s weekly dig</a></li>
<li><a href="http://www.boston.com">boston.com</a></li>
<li><a href="http://www.bostonist.com/">bostonist</a></li>
